      "instruction": "Remove cell culture media. You may wash twice with DPBS at this point."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Remove paraformaldehyde solution."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Remove Triton X-100."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL FITC:TRITC solution"
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL of Anti-Vinculin and blocking buffer mixture."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL of 4 % volume paraformaldehyde solution."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:15:00 ."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Transfer flask to CO 2 incubator."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Label the flask with: Cell line Passage number Date Your intials"
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:05:00 ."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL of 0.1 % volume Triton X-100."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Wash twice with 100 µL washing buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:30:00 ."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL blocking buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Wash twice with washing buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 01:00:00 . Increasing this duration can greatly increase FITC-conjugated secondary antibody binding. It is acceptable to place covered plate in refrigerator overnight. While waiting on this incubation, it is a good time to prepare the combined dye solution."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Remove blocking buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Wash twice with washing buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:30:00 ."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Remove stains."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL of DAPI solution"
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Wash twice with washing buffer."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Remove DAPI."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL PBS to prevent dessication of cells during imaging/storage."
    },
    {
